        "text": "That would be the Reo, priced around ₹59,900."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which model has the best real world range?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "The Primus has the best range at ~107 km."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to charge an Ampere bike to full charge?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Normally 5 to 6 hours. The Nexus charges the fastest at (~3.5 hours)."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Does Ampere provide service coverage?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes - there are over 250 dealers and 5000+ service points throughout India."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Are there any concept models you can pre book?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
